title: Lose Control

description.plain:
“Lose Control” is the second track on I’ve Tried Everything But Therapy by Teddy Swims. Swims uses this song to take everything off his shoulders- losing himself and all control when everything starts caving in; the only way to escape is being with that specific person.

“Lose Control” climbed to No. 1 of Billboard’s Hot 100™ over the course of 32 weeks- making it The longest ascent to the top for a solo male artist in the chart’s 65-year history.
